<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your Order Has Been Accepted - Distro Hub</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f0f8ff;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
      }
      .order-container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 500px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #155724;
        background-color: #d4edda;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 26px;
      }
      p {
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .order-details {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .order-details p {
        margin: 5px 0;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        background-color: #28a745;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #218838;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #888;
      }
      .truck-icon {
        font-size: 50px;
        color: #0056b3;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="order-container">
      <div class="truck-icon">
        <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 640 512"
          width="60"
          height="60"
          fill="#28a745"
        >
          <path
            d="M624 352h-16V243.9c0-12.7-5.1-24.9-14.1-33.9L494 110.1c-9-9-21.2-14.1-33.9-14.1H416V48c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48H48C21.5 0 0 21.5 0 48v320c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h16c0 53 43 96 96 96s96-43 96-96h128c0 53 43 96 96 96s96-43 96-96h48c8.8 0 16-7.2 16-16v-32c0-8.8-7.2-16-16-16zM160 464c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48s21.5-48 48-48 48 21.5 48 48-21.5 48-48 48zm320 0c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48s21.5-48 48-48 48 21.5 48 48-21.5 48-48 48zm80-208H416V144h44.1l99.9 99.9V256z"
          />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1>Your Order Has Been Accepted!</h1>
      <p>
        Great news, <%= shopkeeperName %>! Your recent order with Distro Hub has
        been accepted by the distributor and is now being processed.
      </p>
      <div class="order-details">
        <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= orderId %></p>
        <p><strong>Total Amount:</strong> <%= totalPrice %></p>
        <p><strong>Distributor:</strong> <%= distributorName %></p>
      </div>
      <p>
        Your order is now on the way and should reach you soon. You can track
        your order status by logging into your Distro Hub account.
      </p>
      <a href="http://localhost:3000/orders/<%= orderId %>" class="btn"
        >View Order Details</a
      >
      <br />
      <p>
        If you have any questions about your order, please contact us at
        <a href="mailto:support@distro.com">support@distro.com</a>.
      </p>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Thank you for your business!</p>
        <p>The Distro Hub Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
